title: MS Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 64-bit English integrated March 2014
description:
Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 x64 English only, Integrated March 2014
--------------------------------------------------------------


Source for this release is a original Microsoft Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 64-bit English ISO. 

Integrated Microsoft updates until 13.03.2014 incl. Internet Explorer 11.

- It's the original image from Microsoft except for the added updates and IE11.
- This version is NOT cracked or activated nor otherwise tampered with.


The only program used is WinToolkit1433, which is needed to integrate .net4.5.1 and other POST installation updates.

This release is 100% clean!
Only updates from Microsoft where used.
Feel free to scan for viruses.
I made this DVD for professional use at work.
You may use a original product key from MS

A lot of work has gone in to this and I do hope that there are people out there who will appreciate it.

A list with all the updates that where used is included.

Enjoy
